INSERT INTO WeighBridge (
	Docket,
	WB_Docket,
	Date,
	Rego,
	Supplier,
	Operations,
	Coupe,
	Harvestor,
	Gross,
	Tare,
	GMT,
	Grade,
	Length
)
VALUES (
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.Docket.toString()}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.WB_Docket}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.TransitDate}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.Rego}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.Select_Supplier}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.Select_Operations}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.Select_Coupe}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.Select_Harvestor}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.Gross}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.Tare}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.GMT}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.Select_Grade}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.Select_Length}}'
);
